      we introduced notations for the standard number systems we use in mathematics and discussed 
      their closure properties.
      For this text,
      it is assumed that the reader is familiar with these closure properties and the basic rules of 
      algebra that apply to all real numbers that are given in <xref ref="Ta_propertiesofreals"></xref>.
    </p>


