        </p>
      </introduction>
          <task xml:id="exer_evenoddmulta">
            <statement>
            <p>
              If <m>m</m> is an even integer and <m>n</m> is an integer,
              then <m>m \cdot n</m> is an even integer.
            </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
              <p>
                <tabular>
                  <row bottom="medium" header="yes">
                    <cell right="medium">Step</cell>
                    <cell right="medium">Know</cell>
                    <cell>Know</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row bottom="medium">
                    <cell right="medium"><m>P</m></cell>
                    <cell right="medium"><m>m</m> is an even integer and <m>n</m> is an integer.</cell>
                    <cell>Hypothesis</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row bottom="medium">
                    <cell right="medium"><m>P1</m></cell>
                    <cell right="medium">There exists an integer <m>k</m> <m>m = 2k</m>.</cell>
                    <cell>Definition of an even integer.</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row bottom="medium">
                    <cell right="medium"><m>P2</m></cell>
                    <cell right="medium"><m>m \cdot n = \left( 2k \right) n</m></cell>
                    <cell>Substitution</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row bottom="medium">
                    <cell right="medium"><m>P3</m></cell>
